  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0db8\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf \u0db8\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da4\u0dca\u0da4\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"A group of people are holding firecrackers until Mahinda dies.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former minister Wimalaweera Dissanayake tearfully asked how unfortunate it is that some people in this country, who had celebrated by eating milk rice and lighting firecrackers when the murderer Prabhakaran who drenched the entire country in blood, are waiting for the death of Mahinda Rajapaksa, who led the murder of the murderer Prabhakaran. did",
        "He also mentioned that he wishes not to be born in this world even in the next soul.",
        "Mr. Dissanayake said that he is of the opinion that Mr. Mahinda Rajapaksa is a historical figure who has done a crucial mission for this country regardless of his shortcomings and said that it is an extremely tragic situation for such an ungrateful group of people to wait for such a person to die.",
        "Mr. Wimalaweera Dissanayake also said that he is not a happy person even if an animal dies and not a human being. Even though many people lit firecrackers on the day of Prabhakaran's death in Velupilla, he did not do so because his inner being shows that the death of a human being is not a happy event.",
        "The former minister said that Mr. Mahinda Rajapaksa had spoken to him the day before and said that he is in very good health.",
        "The former minister also said that when he told him about some people's propaganda that he was in a critical condition, Mr. Rajapaksa laughed out loud saying, \"That's it, Wimale..I don't even know that I'm in a critical condition.\""
      ],
